## Alloy Experiment Notes

### Specification Details
- cprr.als: 140 lines modeling full state machine
- Guards as predicates (canAdvanceToTesting, canConfirm, canRefute)
- Invariants as assertions with bounded checking

### Verification Approach
- Bounded model checking: 3 conjectures, 10 steps
- Key properties: confirmedRequiresEvidence, terminalStatesStable

### Decision: Alloy over TLA+
- TLA+ temporal logic unnecessary for structural guards
- Alloy Analyzer visualization aids debugging
- Conjecture #4 (TLA+) abandoned in favor of #8 (Alloy)

